QuestData.Title: The Big Squeeze
QuestData.Description:
So our missin' blue got 'imself dragged off to the big squeeze. Fortunately I am wise to the prise.
We'll soft foot it in like we work there, find your moose, avoid eye contact with the fangs, and chisel out of 'ere like we're masons. Follow?
QuestData.LogDescription: Head to where Cudgelface thinks Huln was taken, and blend in.
